name: Star birth in the extreme
description:
This image is a mosaic of the Carina Nebula assembled from 48 frames taken with Hubble Space Telescope's Advanced Camera for Surveys.

Name:	Carina Nebula, NGC 3372
Type:	Milky Way : Nebula
Distance:	7500 light years
Constellation:	Carina
Category:	Anniversary Nebulae

3,629 editions for the known 3,629 planetary systems to date.

Credit: ESA/Hubble/NASA
